The lawyer for the schoolgirl victims of notorious rapist and killer Paul Bernardo doubts the law can prevent Bernardo from selling an e-novel online. Tim Danson’s statement could increase pressure on e-commerce giant Amazon to remove A MAD World Order.It comes amid outrage from customers who say they will boycott Amazon as long as the book is available.

Paul Bernardo, shown in 1993, is in solitary confinement in Millhaven Institution in Bath, Ont
